lco / listcolour              Lists Axmud standard colour tags
 
   Format:
      ;sco <tag> <colour>     Sets standard <tag> to <colour>
      ;sco <tag>              Resets standard <tag> to its default colour
 
   Notes:
      Axmud's standard colour tags are 'black', 'red', 'green', 'yellow', 
         'blue', 'magenta', 'cyan' and 'white'. The equivalent bold colours are 
         'BLACK', 'RED', 'GREEN', 'YELLOW', 'BLUE', 'MAGENTA', 'CYAN' and 
         'WHITE'.
      This command displays these tags and their colours, which can be modified 
         using the ';setcolour' command.
      See also the help for ';testcolour' and ';addcolourscheme'.

   User commands:
      lco / listcol / listcolor / listcolour
